responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "28C66531412EC53BBF4A8A94BBB411D8", "Wretched beasts! My ancestors once thought they could train them to toil the crops. No doubt this is what led to their demise. I must speak with the local governor and gain the aid of the guard in this matter. For your trouble. There shall be no more. Scamper along, rat.")
